{"tid":998742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90歲夫婦牽手10分鐘內先後離世 女兒悼念：最完美的辭世","createTime":"2019-01-28T07:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T08:02:44.000Z","uid":75969,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb602054d2d532432d279c601c591ab64ea313d9","tid":998742,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190128/_2019012815191240406.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190128%2F_2019012815191240406.jpg&h=d4e6370e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「幾多對持續愛到幾多歲」這一歌詞感動不少人，然而感人的真實故事是存在的。澳洲一對結婚70年的夫婦，在療養院手牽手「同時離世」，連醫生也無法分辨誰先離去。<br />\n<br />\n日前，這對夫妻的女兒阿曼達(Amanda)，在《每日郵報》撰文講述了這感人故事。她指，92歲的父親普拉特爾(Francis Ernest Platell)與90歲的母親諾爾瑪(Norma June Platell)，住在療養院同一間房，兩人只要伸手，就能牽到躺在隔壁床的彼此。阿曼達表示，媽媽1月6日突然呼吸異常，爸爸情況也不穩定，不斷有護理人員進出病房查看情況，不料2人在10分鐘內相繼離世，連醫生也無法判斷誰先走，只好宣布他們是「同時辭世」。<br />\n<br />\n阿曼達表示，患有老人癡呆症(阿茲海默症)的媽媽，病情日漸惡化，連說話能力幾乎失去，阿曼達稱聽到媽媽說的最後一句話是「我的丈夫」，後來失去一切生活能力，媽媽全靠爸爸在旁照料，堅持每天親自替她清洗、喂食，直到後來體力無法負荷，才不得已送進療養院。<br />\n<br />\n阿曼達又指，爸爸曾說「有媽媽的地方就是家」，所以他每天一定會到療養院探望媽媽，兩人一起吃飯、看電視，直到爸爸歷經過一次摔倒，以及輕微中風後，他自己也住進療養院，夫妻兩人住同一間房、床靠著床，伸手就能牽到對方，就這樣陪伴著彼此，直到今年1月6日，一同離開人世。<br />\n<br />\n除了阿曼達外，兩夫婦膝下還有2名兒子和5個孫兒，上周親友們已在喪禮中送別兩人，阿曼達說：「我要感謝上主幫了他們一把，給了他們最完美的辭世，由這個世界去到另一個世界。就像我在悼辭中所說，他們擁有神奇的死亡。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190128/_2019012815191227189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190128%2F_2019012815191227189.jpg&h=9631fc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/921151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F921151&d=wuRAGhAhlQknfzdK5YHn849%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=711f44ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F921151&h=834e6d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/921151</a>"},{"pid":"f582e43eda06b5e7b9d691dbb2bdbf6952d27c81","tid":998742,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"靈魂也可共處"},{"pid":"1e78b9657622c133ad46afa12751b79280f881e4","tid":998742,"uid":217934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"幾多對持續愛到幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4dd5ad56c413517c8131f5b02ab975633368f1","tid":998742,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07633a75d487d3b1ee4cd906b0a87bffb3b3134","tid":998742,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:55:31.000Z","msg":"好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真正貫徹咗&quot;One life, one love&quot;<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"450367c58a8db31f0f7a12dffcf25e2fe8b33d1c","tid":998742,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"the notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340e7b3e055eb441a32a1a31834e59a86eb081cf","tid":998742,"uid":133883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"我諗我到時剩係可以拖自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95caa8f79a35b71a2557483992c6e94969236f4","tid":998742,"uid":70282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"I miss you so much"}]}